Ranger Help for: claim
======================

SYNTAX:      claim
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     250

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to claim a wilderness area as their warden
territory. Claiming territory is a ONE-TIME action that permanently
designates the area as the Ranger's domain. Within claimed territory,
the Ranger receives enhanced bonuses to combat, crafting, and survival
skills. Choose your territory carefully, as this decision cannot be
undone. The high SP cost reflects the significance of this commitment.
